nt Shopping Center and Nyan Lynn Aung and Yadana Mai at Ocean Supercenter (Pazundaung). Ocean Supercenter organized the whole event with Premier Coffee and Herballines as the main sponsors. Co-sponsors were Anlene, Biogesic, Champs, CP, Dentiste’, E-Lan, Top Cashew Brittle and Yum Yum.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/20121208_142953.jpg\"><img title=\"20121208_142953\" src=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/20121208_142953.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"426\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/PZD-Family-Week-8.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-359\" title=\"PZD-Family-Week-(8)\" src=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/PZD-Family-Week-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"401\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/untitled-shoot-001.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-360\" title=\"untitled-shoot-001\" src=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/untitled-shoot-001.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"696\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/PZD-Family-Week-7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-358\" title=\"PZD-Family-Week-(7)\" src=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/PZD-Family-Week-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"401\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/NP-Family-Week-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-356\" title=\"NP-Family-Week-(2)\" src=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/NP-Family-Week-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"446\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/NP-Family-Week-3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-357\" title=\"NP-Family-Week-(3)\" src=\"http://oceansuper