zaar. To make the customers’ children even happier, Ocean Supercenter arranged for a small amusement zone organized by Happy World.</p>\r\n<p>There were two entertainment programs on 8-Dec-2012 at Ocean Supercenter (North Point Branch) and 9-Dec-2012 at Ocean Supercenter (Pazundaung). The customers enjoyed a magic show, a dance performance by models, a product and fashion show but, especially, the game program organized by Dream Boat Entertainment. In the game program, a huge number of customers participated. All the participants were ecstatic as there were many gift give-aways making the occasion even more special. Taking fun to new heights, Ocean Supercenter’s Family Week featured stilt walkers, face-painting and many other fun activities. In the entertainment program, Bunny Phyoe and Athen Cho Swe performed and song their pop songs at North Point Shopping Center and Nyan Lynn Aung and Yadana Mai at Ocean Supercenter (Pazundaung). Ocean Supercenter organized the whole event with Premier Coffee and Herballines  as the main sponsors. Co-sponsors were Anlene, Biogesic, Champs, CP, Dentiste’, E-Lan, Top Cashew Brittle and Yum Yum.</p>\r\n \r\n','Ocean Family Week','City Mart would like invite to our Kids because Santa Claus will visit to City Mart for gift distribution on 23rd, 24th &amp; 25th from 5 pm to 7 pm.','inherit','open','open','','124-revision-6','','','2013-01-07 04:27:01','2013-01-07 04:27:01','',124,'http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/uncategorized/124-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0),(258,1,'2013-01-07 04:46:02','2013-01-07 04:46:02','<p><strong>Business Contact Info:</strong><br/>\r\nCity Mart Holding Co.,Ltd. Head Office : Padonmar Stadium (East Wing), Bargayar Street, Sanchaung Township, Yangon.<br/>\r\nTel: (951) 508460 / 61 / 62<br/>\r\nFax: (951) 512019<br/>\r\nEmail : <a href=\"mailto:enquiry@city.com.mm\">enquiry@city.com.mm</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Recruitment Contact Info:</strong><br/>\r\nCity Mart Holding Co.,Ltd.<br/>\r\nHead Office : Human Reso