,'http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/uncategorized/2-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(460,1,'2013-01-09 07:35:15','2013-01-09 07:35:15','','Our Products','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision-22','','','2013-01-09 07:35:15','2013-01-09 07:35:15','',9,'http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/uncategorized/9-revision-22/',0,'revision','',0),(461,1,'2013-01-18 05:13:14','2013-01-18 05:13:14','<p>With the slogan “Best Value Best Products and More”, Ocean Supercenter is always trying to entertain their customers when shopping. Ocean Family Week was held from the date of 2012 December 5 to 9 at the North Point Shopping Center and the promotion areas of Ocean Supercenter (Pazundaung). In this sales promotion, Ocean Supercenter featured food, Fashion (Men, Women, Kids), Toys, Home Appliances, Electronic Products, Furniture, Kitchen Ware and other popular household items for families.</p>\r\n<p>During the sales promotion program, customers had the chance to win the lucky draw “Gold Prizes” complete with the logo of Ocean Supercenter. On the final day of the sales promotion, the lucky draw winners were selected. They created this event with carnival theme that captured the feeling of a Myanmar bazaar. To make the customers’ children even happier, Ocean Supercenter arranged for a small amusement zone organized by Happy World.</p>\r\n<p>There were two entertainment programs on 8-Dec-2012 at Ocean Supercenter (North Point Branch) and 9-Dec-2012 at Ocean Supercenter (Pazundaung). The customers enjoyed a magic show, a dance performance by models, a product and fashion show but, especially, the game program organized by Dream Boat Entertainment. In the game program, a huge number of customers participated. All the participants were ecstatic as there were many gift give-aways making the occasion even more special. Taking fun to new heights, Ocean Supercenter’s Family Week featured stilt walkers, face-painting and many other fun activities. In the entertainment program, Bunny Phyoe and Athen Cho Swe performed and song their pop songs at North Point Shopping Center and Nyan Lynn Aung and Yadana Mai at Ocean Supercenter (Pazundaung). Ocean Supercenter organized the whole event with Premier Coffee and Herballines as the main sponsors. Co-sponsors were Anlene, Biogesic, Champs, CP, Dentiste’, E-Lan, Top Cashew Brittle and Yum Yum.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/20121208_142953.jpg\"><img title=\"20121208_142953\" src=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/20121208_142953.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"426\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/PZD-Family-Week-8.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-359\" title=\"PZD-Family-Week-(8)\" src=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/PZD-Family-Week-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"401\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/untitled-shoot-001.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-360\" title=\"untitled-shoot-001\" src=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/untitled-shoot-001.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"696\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/PZD-Family-Week-7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-358\" title=\"PZD-Family-Week-(7)\" src=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/PZD-Family-Week-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"401\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/NP-Family-Week-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-356\" title=\"NP-Family-Week-(2)\" src=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/NP-Family-Week-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"446\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://oceansupercenter.com.mm/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/NP-Family-Week-3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-fu