ween 30 to 45 years old</li>\r\n<li>B.E or AGTI -  Mechanical</li>\r\n<li>At least 3 years experience in Mechanical Field</li>\r\n<li>Good Management skills  / Good interpersonal skills</li>\r\n<li>Good leadership skills, communications & interpersonal skills</li>\r\n<li>Computer literate-MS Word, Excel & Power Point, AutoCAD & Email</li>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>2.PROJECT  EXECUTIVE(B.Arch) (3 Posts)</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<li>Between 30 to 45 years old</li>\r\n<li>B. Arch</li>\r\n<li>At least 3 years working experience in related Field</li>\r\n<li>Good leadership skills, communications & interpersonal skills</li>\r\n<li>Computer literate - Auto CAD 2D,3D (compulsory), sketch up (preferable)</li>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>3.PROJECT  EXECUTIVE (Civil) (5 Posts)</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<li>Between 30 to 40 years old</li>\r\n<li>ME(or)B.E (or) AGTI – Civil</li>\r\n<li>At least 3 years working experience in Construction Field (or) Site Management</li>\r\n<li>More prefer AutoCAD knowledge</li>\r\n<li>Good leadership & communications & Site Management skills</li>\r\n<li>Computer literate - MS Office, Power Point, & Email</li>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>4.BRANCH MANAGER (10 Posts)</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<li>Age between 30 to 40 years old</li>\r\n<li>B Sc Degree Holder (or) MBA</li>\r\n<li>At least 5 years managerial experience in retail management (or) consumer product sales management</li>\r\n<li>Good Communications  / Interpersonal & Problem Solving Skills</li>\r\n<li>Must be self motivated, coordination and negotiate with subordinates</li>\r\n<li>To improve Sales, Stock Holding & Stack out , Service & staff management</li>\r\n<li>Computer literate-MS Word, Excel & Power Point</li>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>5.MARKETING EXECUTIVE (3 Posts)</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<li>Age between 25 to 35 years old</li>\r\n<li>MBA or DMA Holder is preferable</li>\r\n<li>Must have at least 3 Yrs Experience in Marketing</li>\r\n<li>Computer Literate - MS Word & Excel</li>\r\n<li>Fluency in English Communication (both in spoken & written)</li>\r\n<li>Must be responsible as the 2nd commander of the Marketing Team</li>\r\n<li>Must have leadership Skill & Team Spirit</li>\r\n<li>Must have the ability to plan in advanced and implement the yearly promotion plan by leading  Team  &  coordination with MKT Mgt</li>\r\n<li>Arrange some emergency action based on the situation happened</li>\r\n<li>Direct Report to Marketing Manager</li>\r\n<li>Good personality and communication skills</li>\r\n<p><br /></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>6.HUMAN RESOURCES EXECUTIVE Female (2 Posts)</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<li>Age between 30 to 35 years old</li>\r\n<li>Degree Holder</li>\r\n<li>At least 2  years experience in HRD field</li>\r\n<li>Good leadership skills, communications & interpersonal skills</li>\r\n<li>Must be self motivated, coordination and negotiate with subordinates</li>\r\n<li>Must have the ability to plan in advanced and implement the yearly recruitment plan by leading  Team  &  coordination with HR Mgt</li>\r\n<li>Computer literate – MS Word,Excel, Power Point & Internet, Email</li>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>7.SENIOR TRAINING  SUPERVISOR Female (2 Posts)</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<li>Age between 24 to 30 years old</li>\r\n<li>Science Degree Holder (or)Fresh MBA/ ABE</li>\r\n<li>At least 2  year Training experience</li>\r\n<li>More prefer translation knowledge</li>\r\n<li>Good communications & interpersonal skills</li>\r\n<li>Computer literate - MS Office ,Power Point & Internet, Email</li>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>8.SENIOR PURCHASING SUPERVISOR (5 Posts)</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<li>Age between 25 to 35 years old</li>\r\n<li>Degree Holder</li>\r\n<li>Must have at least 3 Yrs Experience in dealing with consumer products</li>\r\n<li>Computer Literate - MS Word & Excel</li>\r\n<li>Must be responsible as to plan in Merchandise buying and ordering processes</li>\r\n<li>Must have leadership Skill & Team Spirit</li>\r\n<li>Purchasing plan by leading team & coordination with Manager</li>\r\n<li>Arrange some emergency action based on the situation happened</li>\r\n<li>Good personality and communication skills</li>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>9.Management Trainees</p>\r\n<blockquote><p>\r\n<u>The Qualifications for Management Trainees</u></p>\r\n<li>Education : Any Graduate</li>\r\n<li>Experience : Minimum two years of working experience in any supervisory & management level</li>\r\n<li>Age : Between 22 to 30 years old</li>\r\n<li>Personalities :Good interpersonal skills , neat and tidy appearance</li>\r\n<li>Abilities : Able to work under pressure , share management is a must in skill your competency</li>\r\n<li>Other qualifications : Computer Literate</li>\r\n<p>Note : Fresh Graduates in M.B.A without any experience are also welcome to participate in the program\r\n</p>\r\n<p><u>The Opportunities for Management Trainees</u></p>\r\n<p>The candidates for the programs are entitled to receive the following opportunities in training period :</p>\r\n<li>Training and transportation allowance (During Training)</li>\r\n<li>Leave benefits as per company \'s policies</li>\r\n<li>Commodities discounts in all retail outlets by City Mart</li>\r\n<p>Interested applicants may apply within two weeks after advertisement</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Interested applicants should submit their CVs together with 2 recent photos, copy of NRC, Labour Registration Card, Quarter, Police &amp; Household Registration Card, Graduate Certificates &amp; other relevant testimonials to the following address :</p>\r\n<p>Human Resources Department : City Mart Holding Co. Ltd<br />No. 1-11, Padonmar Stadium (East Wing), Bargayar Street, Sanchaung Township, Yangon, Myanmar.<br />Tel : (951) 508460 / 508 461 / 508 462<br />Fax : (951) 512 019<br />Email : <a href=\"#\">humanresources@city.com.mm</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n','Careers','','inherit','open','open','','200-revision-46','','','2013-11-05 07:39:13','2013-11-05 07:39:13','',200,'http://oceansupercenter.com.mm